#. Description of the plugin
#: autodescription.php
msgid ""
"An automated, advanced, accessible, unbranded and extremely fast SEO solution for your WordPress website."
msgstr ""
"Solusi SEO otomatis, canggih, mudah diakses, tidak bermerek, dan sangat cepat untuk situs WordPress Anda."

#. Author of the plugin
#: autodescription.php
msgid "SGEOBIZ"
msgstr "SGEOBIZ"

#. translators: %1$s = New, lower version number, surrounded in markdown-backticks. %2$s = Old, higher version number, surrounded in markdown-backticks.
#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:375
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Your website has been downgraded successfully to use SGEOBIZ SEO at database version `%1$s` from `%2$s`."
msgstr ""
"Situs web Anda telah berhasil diturunkan versinya untuk menggunakan SGEOBIZ SEO pada versi database `%1$s` dari `%2$s`."

#. translators: %s = Version number, surrounded in markdown-backticks.
#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:426
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Thank you for updating SGEOBIZ SEO! Your website has been upgraded successfully to use SGEOBIZ SEO at database version `%s`."
msgstr ""
"Terima kasih telah memperbarui SGEOBIZ SEO! Situs web Anda telah berhasil ditingkatkan untuk menggunakan SGEOBIZ SEO pada versi database `%s`."

#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:454
msgid ""
"SGEOBIZ SEO automatically optimizes your website for search engines and social media."
msgstr ""
"SGEOBIZ SEO secara otomatis mengoptimalkan situs web Anda untuk mesin pencari dan media sosial."

#. translators: %s = Link, markdown.
#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:458
#, php-format
msgid ""
"To take full advantage of all SEO features, please follow our [5-minute setup guide](%s)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memanfaatkan sepenuhnya semua fitur SEO, ikuti [panduan penyiapan 5 menit](%s) kami."

#. translators: 1: SEO plugin name(s), 2: link to guide, in Markdown!
#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:531
#, php-format
msgid ""
"SGEOBIZ SEO detected metadata from %1$s. Whenever you are set, read our [migration guide](%2$s)."
msgstr ""
"SGEOBIZ SEO mendeteksi metadata dari %1$s. Kapan pun Anda siap, baca [panduan migrasi](%2$s) kami."

#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:667
msgid ""
"Twitter Photo Cards have been deprecated. Your site now uses Summary Cards when applicable."
msgstr ""
"Kartu Foto Twitter sudah tidak digunakan lagi. Situs Anda sekarang menggunakan Kartu Ringkasan bila berlaku."

#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:690
msgid ""
"The previous sitemap timestamp settings have been converted into new global timestamp settings."
msgstr ""
"Setelan stempel waktu peta situs sebelumnya telah diubah menjadi setelan stempel waktu global baru."

#: bootstrap/upgrade.php:782
msgid ""
"The positions in the \"Meta Title Additions Location\" setting for the homepage have been reversed, left to right, but the output has not been changed. If you must downgrade for some reason, remember to switch the location back again."
msgstr ""
"Posisi pada setting \"Lokasi Penambahan Meta Title\" untuk homepage telah dibalik, kiri ke kanan, namun outputnya tidak diubah. Jika Anda harus menurunkan versi karena alasan tertentu, ingatlah untuk mengganti lokasinya kembali."

