#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:47
msgid "Automated Description Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Deskripsi Otomatis"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:50
msgid "Learn how this feature works."
msgstr "Pelajari cara kerja fitur ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:57
msgid "Automatically generate descriptions?"
msgstr "Buat deskripsi secara otomatis?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:63
msgid ""
"Open Graph requires descriptions. So, it's best to leave description generation enabled."
msgstr ""
"Open Graph memerlukan deskripsi. Jadi, sebaiknya biarkan pembuatan deskripsi tetap aktif."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:69
msgid "Advanced Generation Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Generasi Lanjutan"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:72
msgid ""
"The HTML content of your pages can be used to generate descriptions. The generator processes this HTML in passing layers to understand the layout. If the HTML is complex, not all layers may be processed, and you might find spaces missing between sentences. Increasing the maximum number of passes reduces the chance of this happening, but at the cost of performance."
msgstr ""
"Konten HTML halaman Anda dapat digunakan untuk menghasilkan deskripsi. Generator memproses HTML ini secara berlapis untuk memahami tata letaknya. Jika HTML rumit, tidak semua lapisan dapat diproses, dan Anda mungkin menemukan ada spasi yang hilang di antara kalimat. Meningkatkan jumlah operan maksimum akan mengurangi kemungkinan terjadinya hal ini, namun mengorbankan performa."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:82
msgid "Fast (max. 2 passes)"
msgstr "Cepat (maks. 2 lintasan)"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:83
msgid "Accurate (max. 6 passes)"
msgstr "Akurat (maks. 6 lintasan)"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:84
msgid "Thorough (max. 12 passes)"
msgstr "Menyeluruh (maks. 12 lintasan)"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:107
msgid "HTML parsing method:"
msgstr "Metode penguraian HTML:"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/description.php:119
msgid "Learn how this works."
msgstr "Pelajari cara kerjanya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:41
msgid "Content Feed Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Umpan Konten"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:42
msgid ""
"Sometimes, your content can get stolen by robots through the WordPress feeds. This can cause duplicate content issues. To prevent this from happening, it's recommended to convert the feed's content into an excerpt."
msgstr ""
"Terkadang, konten Anda bisa dicuri oleh robot melalui feed WordPress. Hal ini dapat menyebabkan masalah duplikat konten. Untuk mencegah hal ini terjadi, disarankan untuk mengubah konten feed menjadi kutipan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:43
msgid ""
"Adding a backlink below the feed entries will also let the visitors know where the content came from."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan backlink di bawah entri feed juga akan membuat pengunjung mengetahui dari mana konten tersebut berasal."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:48
msgid "Change Feed Settings"
msgstr "Ubah Pengaturan Umpan"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:49
msgid "Convert feed entries into excerpts?"
msgstr "Ubah entri umpan menjadi kutipan?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:50
msgid "By default the excerpt will be at most 400 characters long."
msgstr "Secara default, panjang kutipan maksimal 400 karakter."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:52
msgid "Add link to source below the feed entry content?"
msgstr "Tambahkan tautan ke sumber di bawah konten entri umpan?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:53
msgid "This link will not be followed by search engines."
msgstr "Tautan ini tidak akan diikuti oleh mesin pencari."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:55
msgid "Allow indexing of feeds?"
msgstr "Izinkan pengindeksan feed?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:56
msgid ""
"If this site publishes podcasts, enable this option. Otherwise, leave it disabled. Indexing feeds can cause search engines to crawl and index new pages slower; however, some podcast services require feeds to be indexable."
msgstr ""
"Jika situs ini menerbitkan podcast, aktifkan opsi ini. Jika tidak, biarkan dinonaktifkan. Pengindeksan feed dapat menyebabkan mesin pencari merayapi dan mengindeks halaman baru lebih lambat; namun, beberapa layanan podcast memerlukan feed agar dapat diindeks."

#. translators: %s = Reading Settings URL. Links are in Markdown!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:84
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Note: The feed is already converted into an excerpt through the [Reading Settings](%s)."
msgstr "Catatan: Feed sudah diubah menjadi kutipan melalui [Pengaturan Bacaan](%s)."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/feed.php:96
msgid "View the main feed."
msgstr "Lihat umpan utama."

