#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:87
msgid "Administrative Layout Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Tata Letak Administratif"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:88
msgid "SEO hints and options are displayed throughout the dashboard."
msgstr "Petunjuk dan opsi SEO ditampilkan di seluruh dasbor."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:93
msgid "SEO Bar Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Bilah SEO"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:98
msgid "Display the SEO Bar in overview tables?"
msgstr "Tampilkan Bilah SEO di tabel ikhtisar?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:103
msgid "Display the SEO Bar in the SEO Settings meta box?"
msgstr "Tampilkan Bilah SEO di kotak meta Pengaturan SEO?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:108
msgid "Use a reduced contrast color palette?"
msgstr "Gunakan palet warna kontras yang dikurangi?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:109
msgid "If you find the SEO Bar distracting, this may help you focus better."
msgstr "Jika Anda merasa Bilah SEO mengganggu, ini dapat membantu Anda lebih fokus."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:117
msgid "Use symbols for warnings?"
msgstr "Gunakan simbol untuk peringatan?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:118
msgid ""
"If you have difficulty discerning colors, this may help you spot issues more easily."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda kesulitan membedakan warna, ini dapat membantu Anda mengenali masalah dengan lebih mudah."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:131
msgid "Counter Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Penghitung"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:134
msgid ""
"The pixel counter computes whether the input will fit on search engine result pages."
msgstr ""
"Penghitung piksel menghitung apakah masukan akan sesuai dengan halaman hasil mesin pencari."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:140
msgid "The character counter is based on guidelines."
msgstr "Penghitung karakter didasarkan pada pedoman."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:149
msgid "Display pixel counters?"
msgstr "Tampilkan penghitung piksel?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:154
msgid "Display character counters?"
msgstr "Tampilkan penghitung karakter?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:164
msgid "Option Field Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Bidang Opsi"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:167
msgid "Terms are entries in taxonomies, e.g., Categories and Tags."
msgstr "Istilah adalah entri dalam taksonomi, misalnya Kategori dan Tag."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:176
msgid "Display quick-edit and bulk-edit option fields?"
msgstr "Tampilkan bidang opsi edit cepat dan edit massal?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:181
msgid "Display term-edit option fields?"
msgstr "Tampilkan bidang opsi edit istilah?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:186
msgid "Display user-edit option fields?"
msgstr "Tampilkan bidang opsi edit pengguna?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:193
msgid "Note: Hiding option fields does not remove the data once stored in them."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Menyembunyikan kolom opsi tidak menghapus data yang pernah disimpan di dalamnya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:197
msgid "Performance Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Kinerja"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:198
msgid ""
"Depending on your server's configuration, adjusting these settings can affect performance."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada konfigurasi server Anda, menyesuaikan pengaturan ini dapat memengaruhi kinerja."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:203
msgid "Query Alteration Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Perubahan Kueri"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:205
msgid "Altering the query allows for more control of the site's hierarchy."
msgstr "Mengubah kueri memungkinkan kontrol lebih besar terhadap hierarki situs."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:207
msgid ""
"If your website has thousands of pages, these options can greatly affect database performance."
msgstr ""
"Jika situs web Anda memiliki ribuan halaman, opsi ini dapat sangat memengaruhi kinerja database."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:211
msgid ""
"Altering the query in the database is more accurate, but can increase database query time."
msgstr ""
"Mengubah kueri dalam database lebih akurat, namun dapat menambah waktu kueri database."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:213
msgid ""
"Altering the query on the site is much faster, but can lead to inconsistent pagination. It can also lead to 404 error messages if all queried pages have been excluded."
msgstr ""
"Mengubah kueri di situs jauh lebih cepat, namun dapat menyebabkan penomoran halaman tidak konsisten. Hal ini juga dapat menyebabkan pesan kesalahan 404 jika semua halaman yang ditanyakan telah dikecualikan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:219
msgid "In the database"
msgstr "Di basis data"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:220
msgid "On the site"
msgstr "Di situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:246
msgid "Perform alteration:"
msgstr "Lakukan perubahan:"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:272
msgid "Enable search query alteration?"
msgstr "Aktifkan perubahan kueri penelusuran?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:273
msgid "This allows you to exclude pages from on-site search results."
msgstr "Ini memungkinkan Anda mengecualikan halaman dari hasil pencarian di situs."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:285
msgid "Enable archive query alteration?"
msgstr "Aktifkan perubahan kueri arsip?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:286
msgid "This allows you to exclude pages from on-site archive listings."
msgstr "Hal ini memungkinkan Anda mengecualikan halaman dari daftar arsip di situs."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:296
msgid "Canonical URL Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan URL Kanonik"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:297
msgid "The canonical URL meta tag urges search engines to go to the outputted URL."
msgstr "Tag meta URL kanonik mendesak mesin pencari untuk membuka URL keluaran."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:298
msgid ""
"If the canonical URL meta tag represents the visited page, then the search engine will crawl the visited page. Otherwise, the search engine may go to the outputted URL."
msgstr ""
"Jika meta tag URL kanonik mewakili halaman yang dikunjungi, maka mesin pencari akan meng-crawl halaman yang dikunjungi. Jika tidak, mesin pencari mungkin akan menuju ke URL keluaran."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:302
msgid "Scheme Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Skema"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:303
msgid ""
"If your website is accessible via both HTTP as HTTPS, you may want to set this to HTTPS if not detected automatically. Secure connections are preferred by search engines."
msgstr ""
"Jika situs web Anda dapat diakses melalui HTTP dan HTTPS, Anda mungkin ingin mengaturnya ke HTTPS jika tidak terdeteksi secara otomatis. Koneksi aman lebih disukai oleh mesin pencari."

#. translators: %s = HTTP or HTTPS
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:313
#, php-format
msgid "Detect automatically (%s)"
msgstr "Deteksi secara otomatis (%s)"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:334
msgid "Preferred canonical URL scheme:"
msgstr "Skema URL kanonik pilihan:"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:345
msgid "Paginated Link Relationship Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Hubungan Tautan Paginasi"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:346
msgid ""
"Some search engines look for relations between the content of your pages. If you have pagination on a post or page, or have archives indexed, these options will help search engines look for the right page to display in the search results."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa mesin pencari mencari hubungan antara konten halaman Anda. Jika Anda memiliki penomoran halaman pada postingan atau halaman, atau arsip diindeks, opsi ini akan membantu mesin pencari mencari halaman yang tepat untuk ditampilkan dalam hasil pencarian."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:347
msgid "Enable these options to mitigate duplicated content issues."
msgstr "Aktifkan opsi ini untuk mengurangi masalah duplikat konten."

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:353
msgid "Add `rel` link tags to pages?"
msgstr "Tambahkan tag tautan `rel` ke halaman?"

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:363
msgid "Add `rel` link tags to archives?"
msgstr "Tambahkan tag tautan `rel` ke arsip?"

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:373
msgid "Add `rel` link tags to the homepage?"
msgstr "Tambahkan tag tautan `rel` ke beranda?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:389
msgid "Timestamp Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Stempel Waktu"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:390
msgid "Timestamps help indicate when a page has been published and modified."
msgstr ""
"Stempel waktu membantu menunjukkan kapan suatu halaman telah diterbitkan dan dimodifikasi."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:395
msgid "Timestamp Format Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Format Stempel Waktu"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:396
msgid "This setting determines how specific the timestamp is."
msgstr "Pengaturan ini menentukan seberapa spesifik stempel waktunya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:405
msgid "This outputs the complete date."
msgstr "Ini menampilkan tanggal lengkap."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/general.php:416
msgid ""
"This outputs the complete date including hours, minutes, seconds, and time zone."
