#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:49
msgid "Author pages"
msgstr "halaman penulis"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:53
msgid "Date archives"
msgstr "Arsip tanggal"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:57
msgid "Search pages"
msgstr "Halaman pencarian"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:62
msgid "the entire site"
msgstr "seluruh situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:74
msgid ""
"These options can prevent indexing of the selected archives and pages. If you enable this, search engines will be urged to remove the selected archives or pages from their result pages."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini dapat mencegah pengindeksan arsip dan halaman yang dipilih. Jika Anda mengaktifkan ini, mesin pencari akan diminta untuk menghapus arsip atau halaman yang dipilih dari halaman hasil mereka."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:78
msgid ""
"These options can prevent links from being followed on the selected archives and pages. If you enable this, the selected archives or pages in-page links will gain no SEO value, including your internal links."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini dapat mencegah tautan diikuti pada arsip dan halaman yang dipilih. Jika Anda mengaktifkan ini, arsip atau tautan dalam halaman halaman yang dipilih tidak akan mendapatkan nilai SEO, termasuk tautan internal Anda."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:82
msgid ""
"These options can prevent caching of the selected archives and pages. If you enable this, bots are urged not create a cached copy of the selected archives or pages."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini dapat mencegah penyimpanan cache pada arsip dan halaman yang dipilih. Jika Anda mengaktifkan ini, bot didesak untuk tidak membuat salinan cache dari arsip atau halaman yang dipilih."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:144
msgid "Advanced Query Protection"
msgstr "Perlindungan Kueri Tingkat Lanjut"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:145
msgid ""
"Some URL queries can cause WordPress to show faux archives. When search engines spot these, they will crawl and index them, which may cause a drop in ranking. Advanced query protection will prevent robots from indexing these archives."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa kueri URL dapat menyebabkan WordPress menampilkan arsip palsu. Ketika mesin pencari menemukannya, mereka akan merayapi dan mengindeksnya, yang dapat menyebabkan penurunan peringkat. Perlindungan kueri tingkat lanjut akan mencegah robot mengindeks arsip ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:150
msgid "Enable advanced query protection?"
msgstr "Aktifkan perlindungan kueri tingkat lanjut?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:157
msgid "Paginated Archive Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Arsip Paginasi"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:158
msgid ""
"Paginated archive pages make for lousy landing pages. However, search engines stop looking for links on pages that aren't indexed, and most search engines recognize paginated pages, so keeping them indexed is often useful."
msgstr ""
"Halaman arsip yang diberi halaman menghasilkan halaman arahan yang buruk. Namun, mesin pencari berhenti mencari link pada halaman yang tidak diindeks, dan sebagian besar mesin pencari mengenali halaman yang diberi nomor halaman, sehingga menjaga halaman tersebut tetap terindeks sering kali berguna."

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:165
msgid "Apply `noindex` to every second or later archive page?"
msgstr "Terapkan `noindex` ke setiap halaman arsip kedua atau lebih baru?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:172
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/title.php:257
msgid "This option does not affect the homepage; it uses a different one."
msgstr "Opsi ini tidak memengaruhi beranda; itu menggunakan yang berbeda."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:176
msgid "Copyright Directive Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Petunjuk Hak Cipta"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:177
msgid ""
"Some search engines allow you to control copyright directives on the content they aggregate. It's best to allow some content to be taken by these aggregators, as that can improve contextualized exposure via snippets and previews. When left unspecified, regional regulations may apply. It is up to the aggregator to honor these requests."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa mesin pencari memungkinkan Anda mengontrol arahan hak cipta pada konten yang dikumpulkannya. Sebaiknya izinkan beberapa konten diambil oleh agregator ini, karena hal ini dapat meningkatkan paparan kontekstual melalui cuplikan dan pratinjau. Jika tidak ditentukan, peraturan daerah mungkin berlaku. Terserah agregator untuk memenuhi permintaan ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:182
msgid "Specify aggregator copyright compliance directives?"
msgstr "Tentukan arahan kepatuhan hak cipta agregator?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:189
msgid "Unlimited"
msgstr "Tidak terbatas"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:190
msgid "None, disallow snippet"
msgstr "Tidak ada, larang cuplikan"

#. translators: %d = number
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:195
