msgid "%d character"
msgstr "%d karakter"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:201
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:285
msgid "Standard directive"
msgstr "Arahan standar"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:202
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:286
msgid "Granular directive"
msgstr "Arahan terperinci"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:223
msgid "Maximum text snippet length"
msgstr "Panjang cuplikan teks maksimum"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:227
msgid "This may limit the text snippet length for all pages on this site."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini mungkin membatasi panjang cuplikan teks untuk semua halaman di situs ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:231
msgid ""
"This directive also imposes a limit on meta descriptions and structured data, which unintentionally restricts the amount of information you can share. Therefore, it's best to use at least a 320 character limit."
msgstr ""
"Arahan ini juga menerapkan batasan pada deskripsi meta dan data terstruktur, yang secara tidak sengaja membatasi jumlah informasi yang dapat Anda bagikan. Oleh karena itu, sebaiknya gunakan batas minimal 320 karakter."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:240
msgid "None, disallow preview"
msgstr "Tidak ada, larang pratinjau"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:241
