#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:346
msgid "Warning: No site should enable these options for Posts and Pages."
msgstr ""
"Peringatan: Tidak ada situs yang boleh mengaktifkan opsi ini untuk Postingan dan Halaman."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:379
msgid "Taxonomy Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Taksonomi"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:380
msgid ""
"These settings apply to the taxonomies of post types. When taxonomies have all their bound post types' options checked, they will inherit their status."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini berlaku untuk taksonomi jenis postingan. Ketika taksonomi mencentang semua opsi jenis pos terikatnya, mereka akan mewarisi statusnya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:414
