"Note: A robots.txt file has been detected in the root folder of your website, so these settings have no effect."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: File robots.txt telah terdeteksi di folder root situs web Anda, jadi pengaturan ini tidak berpengaruh."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/robots.php:478
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:240
