"Output supplementary information about your site and every page, such as the title, description, URLs, and language, using a standard search engines can easily understand."
msgstr ""
"Keluarkan informasi tambahan tentang situs Anda dan setiap halaman, seperti judul, deskripsi, URL, dan bahasa, menggunakan mesin pencari standar dapat dengan mudah dipahami."

