#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:58
msgid "Metadata"
msgstr "Metadata"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:63
msgid "Style"
msgstr "Gaya"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:83
msgid "Sitemap Integration Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Integrasi Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:84
msgid ""
"The sitemap is an XML file that lists indexable pages of your website along with optional metadata. It helps search engines find new and updated content quickly."
msgstr ""
"Peta situs adalah file XML yang mencantumkan halaman situs web Anda yang dapat diindeks bersama dengan metadata opsional. Ini membantu mesin pencari menemukan konten baru dan diperbarui dengan cepat."

#. translators: %s = Learn more URL. Markdown!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:90
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The sitemap does not contribute to ranking; [it can only help with indexing](%s). Search engines process smaller, less complicated sitemaps quicker, which shortens the time required for indexing pages."
msgstr ""
"Peta situs tidak berkontribusi terhadap peringkat; [ini hanya dapat membantu pengindeksan](%s). Mesin pencari memproses peta situs yang lebih kecil dan tidak rumit dengan lebih cepat, sehingga mempersingkat waktu yang dibutuhkan untuk mengindeks halaman."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:100
msgid ""
"Note: Another active sitemap plugin has been detected, so the sitemap functionality has been replaced and these settings have no effect."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Plugin peta situs aktif lainnya telah terdeteksi, sehingga fungsi peta situs telah diganti dan pengaturan ini tidak berpengaruh."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:103
msgid ""
"Note: A sitemap has been detected in the root folder of your website, so these settings have no effect."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Peta situs telah terdeteksi di folder akar situs web Anda, jadi pengaturan ini tidak berpengaruh."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:108
msgid "Sitemap Output"
msgstr "Keluaran Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:110
msgid ""
"Search engines crawl links to discover all pages and archives without requiring a sitemap. The optimized sitemap only includes the latest pages and no archives, so search engines can find and process vital changes quickly."
msgstr ""
"Mesin pencari merayapi tautan untuk menemukan semua halaman dan arsip tanpa memerlukan peta situs. Peta situs yang dioptimalkan hanya menyertakan halaman terbaru dan tidak ada arsip, sehingga mesin pencari dapat menemukan dan memproses perubahan penting dengan cepat."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:113
msgid ""
"Disable the optimized sitemap to use complex sitemaps that include all links at the cost of indexing speed."
msgstr ""
"Nonaktifkan peta situs yang dioptimalkan untuk menggunakan peta situs kompleks yang menyertakan semua tautan dengan mengorbankan kecepatan pengindeksan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:119
msgid "Output optimized sitemap?"
msgstr "Keluaran peta situs yang dioptimalkan?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:121
msgid "This sitemap is processed quicker by search engines."
msgstr "Peta situs ini diproses lebih cepat oleh mesin pencari."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:136
msgid "View the base sitemap."
msgstr "Lihat peta situs dasar."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:146
msgid "View the sitemap index."
msgstr "Lihat indeks peta situs."

#. translators: %s = Documentation URL in markdown
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:156
#, php-format
msgid ""
"A multilingual plugin has been detected, so your site may have multiple sitemaps. [Learn more](%s)."
msgstr ""
"Plugin multibahasa telah terdeteksi, sehingga situs Anda mungkin memiliki beberapa peta situs. [Pelajari lebih lanjut](%s)."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:170
msgid "Sitemap Query Limit"
msgstr "Batas Kueri Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:174
msgid "This setting affects how many pages are requested from the database per query."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini mempengaruhi berapa banyak halaman yang diminta dari database per kueri."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:181
msgid ""
"Consider lowering this value when the sitemap shows a white screen or notifies you of memory exhaustion."
msgstr ""
"Pertimbangkan untuk menurunkan nilai ini ketika peta situs menampilkan layar putih atau memberi tahu Anda tentang kehabisan memori."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:186
msgid "Transient Cache Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Cache Sementara"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:187
msgid ""
"To improve performance, generated output can be stored in the database as transient cache."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meningkatkan kinerja, keluaran yang dihasilkan dapat disimpan dalam database sebagai cache sementara."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:192
msgid "Enable sitemap generation cache?"
msgstr "Aktifkan cache pembuatan peta situs?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:193
msgid "Generating the sitemap can use a lot of server resources."
msgstr "Menghasilkan peta situs dapat menggunakan banyak sumber daya server."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:205
msgid "Prerender sitemap via cron?"
msgstr "Pra-render peta situs melalui cron?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:207
msgid ""
"This mitigates timeouts search engines may experience when waiting for the sitemap to render."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini mengurangi waktu tunggu yang mungkin dialami mesin telusur saat menunggu peta situs dirender."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:211
msgid ""
"Only enable prerendering when the sitemap takes longer than 60 seconds to generate."
msgstr ""
"Hanya aktifkan pra-perenderan bila peta situs memerlukan waktu lebih dari 60 detik untuk dibuat."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:227
msgid ""
"The robots.txt output is the first thing search engines look for before crawling your site. If you add the sitemap location in that output, then search engines may automatically access and index the sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Output robots.txt adalah hal pertama yang dicari mesin pencari sebelum meng-crawl situs Anda. Jika Anda menambahkan lokasi peta situs pada keluaran tersebut, maka mesin telusur dapat secara otomatis mengakses dan mengindeks peta situs tersebut."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:228
msgid ""
"If you do not add the sitemap location to the robots.txt output, you should notify search engines manually through webmaster-interfaces provided by the search engines."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak menambahkan lokasi peta situs ke keluaran robots.txt, Anda harus memberi tahu mesin telusur secara manual melalui antarmuka webmaster yang disediakan oleh mesin telusur."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:245
msgid ""
"Note: You're using the plain permalink structure; so, no robots.txt file can be generated."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Anda menggunakan struktur tautan permanen biasa; jadi, tidak ada file robots.txt yang dapat dibuat."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:263
msgid "Sitemap Hinting"
msgstr "Petunjuk Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:267
msgid "Add sitemap location to robots.txt?"
msgstr "Tambahkan lokasi peta situs ke robots.txt?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:282
msgid "Timestamps Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Stempel Waktu"

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:285
msgid ""
"The `<lastmod>` tag shows the last updated time of a page. It helps search engines to quickly find content changes via the sitemap."
msgstr ""
"Tag `<lastmod>` menunjukkan waktu terakhir halaman diperbarui. Ini membantu mesin pencari dengan cepat menemukan perubahan konten melalui peta situs."

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:293
msgid "Add `<lastmod>` to the sitemap?"
msgstr "Tambahkan `<lastmod>` ke peta situs?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:303
msgid "Sitemap Styling Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Gaya Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:304
msgid ""
"You can style the sitemap to give it a more personal look for your visitors. Search engines do not use these styles."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menata peta situs untuk memberikan tampilan yang lebih pribadi bagi pengunjung Anda. Mesin pencari tidak menggunakan gaya ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:305
msgid ""
"Note: Changes may not appear to have an effect directly because the stylesheet is cached in the browser for 30 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Perubahan mungkin tidak berdampak langsung karena stylesheet di-cache di browser selama 30 menit."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:309
msgid "Enable Styling"
msgstr "Aktifkan Gaya"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:314
msgid "Style sitemap?"
msgstr "Peta situs gaya?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:314
msgid "This makes the sitemap more readable for humans."
msgstr "Hal ini membuat peta situs lebih mudah dibaca oleh manusia."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:330
msgid "Sitemap Header Background Color"
msgstr "Warna Latar Belakang Header Peta Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:339
msgid "Sitemap Title and Lines Color"
msgstr "Judul Peta Situs dan Warna Garis"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:348
msgid "Header Title Logo"
msgstr "Logo Judul Tajuk"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:353
msgid "Show logo next to sitemap header title?"
msgstr "Tampilkan logo di samping judul header peta situs?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/sitemaps.php:369
msgid "Setting a logo requires JavaScript."
msgstr "Menyetel logo memerlukan JavaScript."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:67
msgid "Post Dates"
msgstr "Tanggal Posting"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:84
msgid "Social Meta Tags Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Tag Meta Sosial"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:85
msgid ""
"Output various meta tags for social site integration, among other third-party services."
msgstr ""
"Keluarkan berbagai tag meta untuk integrasi situs sosial, di antara layanan pihak ketiga lainnya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:98
msgid "Output Open Graph meta tags?"
msgstr "Keluarkan tag meta Grafik Terbuka?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:99
msgid ""
"Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest and many other social sites make use of these meta tags."
msgstr ""
"Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest dan banyak situs sosial lainnya menggunakan meta tag ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:104
msgid ""
"Note: Another Open Graph plugin has been detected. These meta tags might conflict."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Plugin Open Graph lainnya telah terdeteksi. Tag meta ini mungkin bertentangan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:110
msgid "Output Facebook meta tags?"
msgstr "Keluarkan tag meta Facebook?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:111
msgid "Output various meta tags targeted at Facebook."
msgstr "Keluarkan berbagai meta tag yang ditargetkan di Facebook."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:120
msgid "Output Twitter Card meta tags?"
msgstr "Keluarkan tag meta Kartu Twitter?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:121
msgid ""
"X (formerly Twitter), Discord, LinkedIn, and some other networks make use of these meta tags."
msgstr ""
"X (sebelumnya Twitter), Discord, LinkedIn, dan beberapa jaringan lain menggunakan tag meta ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:126
msgid ""
"Note: Another Twitter Card plugin has been detected. These meta tags might conflict."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Plugin Twitter Card lainnya telah terdeteksi. Tag meta ini mungkin bertentangan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:132
msgid "Output oEmbed scripts?"
msgstr "Keluarkan skrip oEmbed?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:133
msgid ""
"WordPress, Discord, Drupal, Squarespace, and many other clients can make use of these scripts."
msgstr ""
"WordPress, Discord, Drupal, Squarespace, dan banyak klien lainnya dapat menggunakan skrip ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:141
msgid "Social Title Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Judul Sosial"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:142
msgid ""
"Most social sites and third-party services automatically include the website URL inside their embeds. When the site title is described well in the site URL, including it in the social title will be redundant."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar situs sosial dan layanan pihak ketiga secara otomatis menyertakan URL situs web di dalam penyematannya. Jika judul situs dijelaskan dengan baik di URL situs, memasukkannya ke dalam judul sosial akan menjadi mubazir."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:145
msgid ""
"When you provide a custom Open Graph or Twitter title, the site title will be omitted automatically."
msgstr ""
"Saat Anda memberikan judul Open Graph atau Twitter khusus, judul situs akan dihilangkan secara otomatis."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:153
msgid "Remove site title from generated social titles?"
msgstr "Hapus judul situs dari judul sosial yang dihasilkan?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:162
msgid ""
"A social image can be displayed when a link to your website is shared. It is a great way to grab attention."
msgstr ""
"Gambar sosial dapat ditampilkan ketika tautan ke situs web Anda dibagikan. Ini adalah cara yang bagus untuk menarik perhatian."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:170
msgid "Output multiple Open Graph image tags?"
msgstr "Keluarkan beberapa tag gambar Open Graph?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:171
msgid ""
"This enables users to select any image attached to the page shared on social networks, like Facebook."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini memungkinkan pengguna untuk memilih gambar apa pun yang dilampirkan pada halaman yang dibagikan di jejaring sosial, seperti Facebook."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:179
msgid "Social Image Fallback URL"
msgstr "URL Pengganti Gambar Sosial"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:180
msgid ""
"When no image is available from the page or term, this fallback image will be used instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada gambar yang tersedia dari halaman atau istilah tersebut, gambar cadangan ini akan digunakan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:196
msgid "Theme Color Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Warna Tema"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:197
msgid ""
"Discord styles embeds with the theme color. The theme color can also affect the tab-color in some browsers."
msgstr ""
"Gaya perselisihan disematkan dengan warna tema. Warna tema juga dapat mempengaruhi warna tab di beberapa browser."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:201
msgid "Theme Color"
msgstr "Warna Tema"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:209
msgid "Site Shortlink Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Tautan Pendek Situs"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:210
msgid ""
"The shortlink tag can be manually used for microblogging services like Twitter, but it has no SEO value whatsoever."
msgstr ""
"Tag shortlink dapat digunakan secara manual untuk layanan mikroblog seperti Twitter, namun tidak memiliki nilai SEO apa pun."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:215
msgid "Output shortlink tag?"
msgstr "Tag tautan pendek keluaran?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:226
msgid "https://www.facebook.com/YourBusinessProfile"
msgstr "https://www.facebook.com/ProfilBisnisAnda"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:228
msgid "Facebook Integration Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Integrasi Facebook"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:229
msgid ""
"Facebook post sharing works mostly through Open Graph. However, you can also link your Business and Personal Facebook pages, among various other options."
msgstr ""
"Berbagi kiriman Facebook sebagian besar berfungsi melalui Open Graph. Namun, Anda juga dapat menautkan halaman Facebook Bisnis dan Pribadi Anda, di antara berbagai opsi lainnya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:230
msgid ""
"When these options are filled in, Facebook might link the Facebook profile to be followed and liked when your post or page is shared."
msgstr ""
"Ketika opsi ini diisi, Facebook mungkin menautkan profil Facebook untuk diikuti dan disukai ketika postingan atau halaman Anda dibagikan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:236
msgid "Facebook Publisher page"
msgstr "Halaman Penerbit Facebook"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:240
msgid "Only Facebook Business Pages are accepted."
msgstr "Hanya Halaman Bisnis Facebook yang diterima."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:252
msgid "Facebook Author Fallback Page"
msgstr "Halaman Pengganti Penulis Facebook"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:256
