msgstr "Profil Facebook Anda."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:262
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:376
msgid "Authors can override this option on their profile page."
msgstr "Penulis dapat mengganti opsi ini di halaman profil mereka."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:271
msgid "@your-site-username"
msgstr "@ nama pengguna-situs-Anda"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:274
msgid "@your-personal-username"
msgstr "@ nama pengguna-pribadi Anda"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:278
msgid "Twitter Integration Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Integrasi Twitter"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:279
msgid ""
"Sharing posts on X (formerly Twitter) works mostly via Twitter Cards and may fall back to use Open Graph. However, you can also link your Business and Personal X pages, among various other options."
msgstr ""
"Berbagi postingan di X (sebelumnya Twitter) sebagian besar berfungsi melalui Twitter Cards dan mungkin kembali menggunakan Open Graph. Namun, Anda juga dapat menautkan halaman Bisnis dan Pribadi X, di antara berbagai opsi lainnya."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:288
msgid ""
"When you share a link on X (formerly Twitter), an image can appear on the side or as a large cover."
msgstr ""
"Saat Anda membagikan tautan di X (sebelumnya Twitter), gambar dapat muncul di samping atau sebagai sampul besar."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:291
msgid ""
"The Twitter Card type also affects images in Discord embeds; either displayed small at the side or large below."
msgstr ""
"Jenis Kartu Twitter juga memengaruhi gambar di penyematan Discord; baik ditampilkan kecil di samping atau besar di bawah."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:325
msgid "Learn more about this card."
msgstr "Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang kartu ini."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:342
msgid "Card and Content Attribution"
msgstr "Atribusi Kartu dan Konten"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:344
msgid ""
"X (formerly Twitter) claims users will be able to follow and view the profiles of attributed accounts directly from the card when these fields are filled in."
msgstr ""
"X (sebelumnya Twitter) mengklaim pengguna akan dapat mengikuti dan melihat profil akun yang diatribusikan langsung dari kartu ketika kolom ini diisi."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:345
msgid "However, for now, these fields seem to have no discernible effect."
msgstr ""
"Namun, untuk saat ini, bidang-bidang tersebut tampaknya tidak mempunyai pengaruh yang nyata."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:350
msgid "Website Twitter Profile"
msgstr "Profil Twitter Situs Web"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:354
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:370
msgid "Find your @username."
msgstr "Temukan @namapengguna Anda."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:366
msgid "Twitter Author Fallback Profile"
msgstr "Profil Pengganti Penulis Twitter"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:384
msgid "oEmbed Settings"
msgstr "oSematkan Pengaturan"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:385
msgid ""
"Some social sharing services and clients, like WordPress, LinkedIn, and Discord, obtain the linked page information via oEmbed."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa layanan dan klien berbagi sosial, seperti WordPress, LinkedIn, dan Discord, memperoleh informasi halaman tertaut melalui oEmbed."

#. translators: Unavailable means that either a custom Open Graph title is missing or Open Graph is disabled.
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:392
msgid "This will fall back to the meta title if the Open Graph title is unavailable."
msgstr "Ini akan kembali ke judul meta jika judul Open Graph tidak tersedia."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:400
msgid "Use Open Graph title?"
msgstr "Gunakan judul Grafik Terbuka?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:401
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want to replace page titles with Open Graph titles in embeds."
msgstr ""
"Centang opsi ini jika Anda ingin mengganti judul halaman dengan judul Open Graph di penyematan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:407
msgid ""
"Only custom social images that are selected via the Media Library are considered."
msgstr ""
"Hanya gambar sosial khusus yang dipilih melalui Perpustakaan Media yang dipertimbangkan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:414
msgid "Use social image?"
msgstr "Gunakan citra sosial?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:415
msgid ""
"LinkedIn displays the post's featured image in embeds. Check this option if you want to replace it with the social image."
msgstr ""
"LinkedIn menampilkan gambar unggulan postingan dalam penyematan. Centang opsi ini jika Anda ingin menggantinya dengan gambar sosial."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:423
msgid "Remove author name?"
msgstr "Hapus nama penulis?"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:424
msgid ""
"Discord shows the page author's name above the sharing embed. Check this option if you find this undesirable."
msgstr ""
"Discord menunjukkan nama penulis halaman di atas penyematan berbagi. Centang opsi ini jika Anda merasa ini tidak diinginkan."

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:431
msgid "Post Date Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Tanggal Posting"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:432
msgid ""
"Some social sites output the shared post's publishing and modified data in the sharing snippet."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa situs sosial menampilkan penerbitan postingan bersama dan data yang dimodifikasi dalam cuplikan berbagi."

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:443
msgid "Add `article:published_time` to posts?"
msgstr "Tambahkan `artikel: waktu_diterbitkan` ke postingan?"

#. translators: the backticks are Markdown! Preserve them as-is!
#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/social.php:452
msgid "Add `article:modified_time` to posts?"
msgstr "Tambahkan `artikel:modified_time` ke postingan?"

