msgid "Example Category"
msgstr "Contoh Kategori"

#: inc/views/settings/metaboxes/title.php:79
msgid ""
"The page title is prominently shown within the browser tab as well as within the search engine results pages."
msgstr ""
"Judul halaman ditampilkan dengan jelas di tab browser dan juga di halaman hasil mesin pencari."

